<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ko<supplied reason="omitted">p</supplied>parakecaripaṉmaṟkku yāṇṭu 3<g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu piramateyam Īcāṉamaṅkalattu paruṭaiyom Ivūr tiruccen<note n="322-2">The stone is broken at this end.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>y<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied> kaṟṟaḷiy perumāṉaṭikaḷukku tevatāṉamāka Eṅkaḷ paruṭai nilattaiy niroṭu Aṭṭi ku<unclear>ṭu</unclear>tta nilattu<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>ku Ic<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> tta Ellai mekkiṉukku Ellaiy Amaṇkuṭi Ūr E<unclear>l</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>kiḻ<hi rend="grantha">ai</hi> teruviṉukku kiḻakkum kiḻakkiṉukku Ellaiy pāratāyaṉ nakkaṉ cātta ṉuḷḷiṭṭārum pātakāri marutañ centaṉum Āveṇi nārāyaṇa nārāyaṇaṉum Āvaṇi <unclear>ce</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>lattukku me<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kkum vaṭakkiṉukku Ellaiy kāccuvaṉ ka<hi rend="grantha">ṇṇa</hi> nakkaṉu maiyittiraiyaṉ nārāyaṇa<unclear>ṉ</unclear> murukaṉ Uḷḷiṭṭārum pāratāyaṉ nārāyaṇa nakkaṉum pārata <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>ṭṭār nilattukku teṟkum teṟkiṉukku Ellaiy maṟavaṉvāykku vaṭakkum Ivvi<unclear>c</unclear>aitta paṉṉāṉkellaiyuḷ Akappaṭṭa paruṭainilam <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

